<blog>
# eplus-admin-server 

## 1. 

### 
`eplus-admin-server`  Spring Boot CRMDMSFMSWMS 

### 
- 
-  API 
- 
- 

### 
- 
- 
- 
- DevOps 

---

## 2. 

### 
 **Modular Monolith** Spring Boot 

#### 
- **yudao-server**
- **yudao-framework** Starter
- **eplus-module-\***CRMDMSFMSWMS 
- **yudao-module-\***
- **eplus-flyway**
- **yudao-dependencies**

### 
- **** `@SpringBootApplication(scanBasePackages)` 
- **API  Biz ** `-api`  `-biz` 
- **DDD **Controller  Service  Convert  Mapper  DO
- **SPI ** `spring.factories` 

### 
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[] --> B[API Gateway]
    B --> C[yudao-server]
    C --> D[yudao-module-system]
    C --> E[yudao-module-bpm]
    C --> F[eplus-module-crm]
    C --> G[eplus-module-dms]
    C --> H[eplus-module-fms]
    C --> I[eplus-module-wms]
    C --> J[yudao-framework]
    J --> K[Security]
    J --> L[DataPermission]
    J --> M[Desensitize]
    J --> N[OperateLog]
    J --> O[Redis/MQ/Job]
    C --> P[(MySQL)]
```

### 
```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Client[/] -->|HTTP| Controller[Controller]
    Controller -->|VO| Convert[Convert]
    Convert -->|DO| Service[Service]
    Service -->|Mapper| Mapper[MyBatis Mapper]
    Mapper -->|SQL| DB[(MySQL)]
    DB --> Mapper
    Mapper --> Service
    Service --> Convert
    Convert -->|DTO| Controller
    Controller -->|Response| Client
```

---

## 3. 

### 

- [YudaoServerApplication.java](yudao-server/src/main/java/cn/iocoder/yudao/server/YudaoServerApplication.java)


```java
@SpringBootApplication(scanBasePackages = {
    "${yudao.info.base-package}.server",
    "${yudao.info.base-package}.module",
    "${eplus.info.base-package}.module"
})
```

###

|--------|--------|------|
|  | CRM | `eplus-module-crm` |
|  |  | `yudao-module-system` |
|  |  | `yudao-framework` |

###

- Flowable

###

graph TD
